const Notes = () => { return
  • Hide these notes
  • Commit events branch
  • Set up routine:
    • Work (08:30 - 12:30, Mon-Fri)
    • Work (13:30 - 17:30, Mon-Fri)
    • Prepare for sleep (22:45 - 23:30)
    • Sleep (23:30 - 06:50)
  • List projects
  • Start noting how much time I give each project (click once for each 15 minutes?)
  • Sort them so that the ones with the smaller time accumulation come earlier in list
  • Each interim block of time should trigger suggestions for things that might usefully be done in that time
  • Time after work should start with a status check: "I'm done", "I'm raring to go!", etc and then tailor suggestions accordingly
  • Todo items should get days of week for which they are applicable
  • Todo items should get repeating schedule?
  • I would like to mark work as not showing, but instead show time between work and a scheduled event
  • Track bedtime and time for prep and show available time after other events
  • "Refill pill containers" repeats every 10 days
  • The trash/recycling & laundry todos repeat on particular days of the week
  • "Pay rent" occurrs on the first of each month
  • Times should display with two digits on each side of the colon
  • Perhaps I should be storing start & end times rather than start and duration?
  • Projects:
    • Health
    • Parents
    • Omni Federal
    • DoNext
    • Pirates of Penzance
    • Macbeth
    • Arisia '23 Tech
